reviews.name: Keytronic KT400P1 104-Key PS2 Keyboard, Beige
reviews.reviewText: This is the full size model Keytronic keyboard and it works great. Just be aware that full size means fulll size as in slightly larger than normal. Also, to me, they keys are slightly "loose" feeling, but this keyboard does in fact feel good when typing and is a good keyboard for daily constant use.
reviews.title: It's a Keytronic

reviews.name: Keytronic KT400P1 104-Key PS2 Keyboard, Beige
reviews.reviewText: This keyboard is fine if one is interested is a standard keyboard. I was (am) looking for a larger keyboard and thought this one was going to be. But....it's no different from what I'm currently using. It's a really good value and if one simply needs to replace what they're using, it should be be fine for them. I, however, returned mine cause it just wasn't what I'm looking for.
reviews.title: 05 August 2011

reviews.name: Keytronic KT400P1 104-Key PS2 Keyboard, Beige
reviews.reviewText: Arrived before expected, p/u at store was quick and painless. This is a great value for the price.
reviews.title: For a PS/2 solution this K/B and mouse are great
